reviewText: Every movie was great, thank you.
Love all four of the movies was a great buy
Four DVDs without a single scratch. Work great in both DVD and Blu Ray players.
Great movies action all the way

I only watched the Kingdom of Heaven which is why I ordered it.  I"ve been looking for this DVD for a long long time.  I loved the moral of the story.  A person would have to not let the time of history be a problem for them.........I ate it up and have watched it about six times in a week.  It took me a few times before I could easily absorb it all.
